[3] Ukraine
Date: Tue 3 Jan 2012
Source: Den (Ukraine Daily, Ukrinform [In Russian, machine translation - edited]
http://www.day.kiev.ua/3035136


Number of suspected cases of measles number almost 1500
---------------------------------------------------
The total number of suspected cases of measles in Ukraine has reached 1472 since the beginning of the outbreak according to data released to the press by the Ministry of Health.

In the western regions suspected cases now number 1395, with 59 in the Volyn region, 31 in Carpathian, 296 in Ivano-Frankivsk, 959 in Lviv, Lviv, and 50 in Rivne.

As of Tue 3 Jan 2012, 9 suspected cases have been recorded in Kiev. The number of reported cases in other regions is 79.

Since the beginning of 2011, the number of cases of measles has risen to 1667.

